{"tid":2405070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：新年第一咒 - 皇天擊殺港共納粹。皇天擊殺醫官禽獸。港共納粹鷹犬爪牙，早死早着落地獄！","createTime":"2021-02-12T06:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T01:09:06.000Z","uid":37112,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"270996b9e29c3c4aa880daeab6141dae99491d3c","tid":2405070,"uid":37112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"陳雲：皇天擊殺港共納粹。皇天擊殺醫官禽獸。迫害人民停課、停業、停市、檢測、拘留、封樓、探熱、嘟碼之港共納粹鷹犬爪牙，早死早着落地獄，全家閻羅王報到，地獄永劫煎熬，出苦無期。<br />\n福氣來自天理，天理來自是非辨別，恩怨分明。不辨是非，不分恩怨，無福可言。此乃陳雲辛丑開年第一咒。今年不賀年，皇天擊殺不義。儒門大義、華夏道統由此保存。"},{"pid":"db8d72974a0e988db5b02fe13ac66aa4e1943103","tid":2405070,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nBxbf7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnBxbf7X.jpg&h=f5bda33d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MciawGi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMciawGi.jpg&h=55a7d13c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRFcK1j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRFcK1j.jpg&h=6ad115cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/H2usLUF.jpg&amp;h=c8e3ef10&amp;s=540\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CKJmCtT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCKJmCtT.jpg&h=7a981f12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfe35676f04192aae153ba4d4b9f0ca15c9e7a94","tid":2405070,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"明明佢專屌政府 <br />\n<br />\nd黃絲精神病又屈佢唔會屌政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}